ERNESTO & HEATHER! 💍 
When I first met these two a couple years ago (we shared an uber together one night in LA with a mutual friend) I was instantly struck by their incredible positive energy and very apparent love for one another. 
We immediatley joked that someday I would make them an engagment ring! 💎

While I never saw them again after that one Uber ride (they returned home to Louisiana) they nevertheless left an indelible mark.  If you ever meet them you’ll quickly know what i mean - they have such a great energy and zest for life.  It’s contagious. 🫶🏼

So when Ernesto messaged me this summer and said it might be time to start planning a ring I was delighted to say the least.  And then 2 months later to be one of their first phone calls after a storybook proposal in Sicily was just another reminder why I’m convinced I have one of the best jobs in the world! 
Here’s to a life of Health and Happiness! 🙏🏼 #engagementring

DANIEL & TEAL! 💍
Having known Daniel for 12 years I knew he must’ve met someone special when he posted an IG story featuring Teal relatively soon after they started seeing each other. 

You see, Daniel is not the type of guy to just post random girls or casual flings so I immediately knew that in Teal he had found something different. Much different. 🫶🏼

I jokingly DM’d him a Ring emoji to one of these very first stories and he immediatley replied with “HIGHLY POSSIBLE.”
It thus came as no surprise when a few short months later, Daniel was already sending me ring inspirations.  I knew we were off to the races. 🎉 
When I finally met Teal and saw the two of them together I could instantly see how solid of a partnership they had already formed.  The ring was just a formality. 
Thank you both for trusting me with such an important milestone.  It was an honor and privilege to make your engagement ring.  I wish you nothing but a life of great health & continued happiness!
Mazel Tov! 💍🙌🏼 #engagementring

Delivered just in time for Christmas!🎄Would you say YES?! #engagementring 🎅🏽

BRAD & ANNA!💍❤️
Wow! Where do I even begin?! Keep reading and I’ll try my best…
After being best friends with Brad for over 10 years I must admit that we had both started to question whether either one of us would ever meet, “THE ONE.”
You see Brad and I have been through it all together… ups and downs, successes and failures, and more heartache than we’d care to admit.  Through these trials and tribulations, however, Brad has never wavered in his desire to eventually meet a wife and start a family. And I’ve always admired that. 

And just as that continuous glimmer of hope was starting to fade a little, Brad was introduced to Anna Herrin.  And  in an instant, EVERYTHING had changed. 
The first thing we said to each other was “Let’s not fuck this one up!” 
That’s because it was obvious from day one that Anna was different. Much different. 
She was funny, she was kind, she was talented and she was beautiful… but most importantly she was a perfect partner… and she immediately made Brad’s house a HOME.🏡They just clicked… When you know, you KNOW. 
Fast forward to this Christmas when I finally got THE CALL… “It’s time to make the ring!” 

Little did I know we would not just be making ONE ring rather TWO RINGS… both completely bespoke and departing from traditional convention. 🙌🏼
On Christmas Day, Brad & Anna were engaged at their seaside estate in Cape Elizabeth Maine when he proposed with a stunning yellow gold bezel set solitaire…  And then a few short hours later, Brad shocked Anna again with an incredible 13 carat emerald cut eternity band… truly a Christmas to remember!! 🍾🍾
It gives me great pleasure to wish both Brad & Anna a life filled with endless joy, laughter, adventure and good health. 
Congratulations on finding each other. I love you both!  Mazel Tov! ❤️#engagementring
